{"tid":653951,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點樣可以證明資料當事人無法親身提交申請證據?","createTime":"2018-05-05T07:53:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-06T11:46:58.000Z","uid":170309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6455f465165ee9714c5f993061ee04cf67ea64a8","tid":653951,"uid":170309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T07:53:57.000Z","msg":"想問入境事務處婚姻登記處拿d資料?<br />\n遲d唔係香港....我授權人代領<br />\n其中有樣野要交 -<br />\n「資料當事人身在香港以外的地方，或身在香港但能證明無法親身遞交申請及／或領取申請結果的證據」<br />\n<br />\n係咪我係外國打個卡影張相定俾著機票佢睇就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5adb48260aa1a8ec9b1cb83ab39ea85ccb9c99e6","tid":653951,"uid":170309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T11:52:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3438723c8d6069fbcac257f814e53e0c58336ffd","tid":653951,"uid":170309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5adb48260aa1a8ec9b1cb83ab39ea85ccb9c99e6","tid":653951,"uid":170309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T11:52:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T13:06:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbc4490e21e921f06520cbe8f15a414810847bbd","tid":653951,"uid":170309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T11:46:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}